#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Package Item gspec
# URL: http://englishlive.ef.com/it-it/offerta-inglese/
# Date : 16/11/2016
# an Item has :
#             .header [  .nagging, h2 ,.desc, .pricing, .cta, .disclaimer]
#             .footer [  ul li] a list of them some active and some no but there must be at least 1
#               disclaimer should be in 2 lines in desktop view H 28 pixel and one line on Tab/mob 14 pixel
#
# see https://github.com/galenframework/workshop-shopping-cart/blob/master/galen-tests/specs/cart-item.spec
# TODO add test for disclaimer being in 2 lines
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# # $('.package .header h2')
@objects
    headerH2                             css      .header h2
    headerDesc                           css      .header .desc
    headerPricing                        css      .header .pricing
    headerCta                            css      .header .cta
    headerdisclaimer                     css      .header .disclaimer
    footer-item-*                        css      .footer ul li
#
# ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
# Set values
#@@ set noOfPackages         ${count("item-*")}
#@@ set lastPackItemNo       cart-item-${noOfPackages}
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
= package item =
     @on mobile
         headerdisclaimer:
                          height 10 to 50 px

     @on desktop
         headerdisclaimer:
                          height 10 to 50 px

     @on *
         headerH2, headerDesc, headerPricing, headerPricing, headerCta, headerdisclaimer,  footer-item-1 :
                                                                                                         inside parent
                                                                                                         visible

